00:00:18.330 --> 00:00:20.930
years, ever since I
started.

00:00:20.930 --> 00:00:23.461
Mike is the Egan Professor of Management at
the Wharton School and has

00:00:23.461 --> 00:00:28.500
been teaching there for 15 years or so.
