00:05:19.870 --> 00:05:26.159
be it may not be very good.
Other end of the spectrum, analysis paralysis,

00:05:26.159 --> 00:05:29.020
perfect decision.
It just took a long time to reach it.

00:05:29.020 --> 00:05:35.770
We want to find the sweet spot somehow in-between.
We want it to be good and timely.

