00:05:47.330 --> 00:05:51.040
people that you have admired in politics or
at this company or in the

00:05:51.040 --> 00:05:56.629
community, they have made.
Start thinking about what makes for good and

00:05:56.629 --> 00:06:00.180
timely decisions.
This is about making decisions when somebody

00:06:00.180 --> 00:06:06.050
else is looking to you for
the leadership you are obliged to exercise.

00:06:06.050 --> 00:06:09.910
To get us going, on the premise that I think
we often think about these

00:06:09.910 --> 00:06:16.469
issues most tangibly, which also means most
memorably, if we can see

00:06:16.469 --> 00:06:20.449
these ideas embedded in experience, your own
