this question, Paul, or
Jenny for that matter, I challenge you -- I

00:06:29.870 --> 00:06:33.009
think you're not going to
be able to answer this question to help us

00:06:33.009 --> 00:06:37.169
remember who Gustavus W.
Smith is.

00:06:37.169 --> 00:06:41.260
Gustavus W. Smith.
This is really a -- this is a tough one.

